README
====================

The module allows for reading barcode information from images, and fetches extended information from www.upcdatabase.com.

This Ruby module makes use of the following libraries:
	- The RJB Ruby gem from http://rjb.rubyforge.org/
	- ZXing Java barcode library from http://code.google.com/p/zxing/
		The pre-built jars are included for convenience
		
Example Usage:

include 'upc_scanner'
result = UpcScanner::Scanner.read('test/test.gif')
puts result.inspect